-iron-ore-customs-clearance-sources-2024-01-23/</link><description>据知情人士透露，来自全球第四大供应商福蒂斯丘金属集团的至少两批铁矿石货物在中国北方曹妃甸港因固体废物检查而面临异常海关延误。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 11:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/fortescue-faces-rare-delays-china-iron-ore-customs-clearance-sources-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：大型科技公司报告，中国得到控制，日本央行保持冷静</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-23/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 11:04:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>“滚雪球”衍生品助长中国股市雪崩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/snowball-derivatives-feed-chinas-stock-market-avalanche-2024-01-23/</link><description>中国股市暴跌导致与该国股指相关的衍生品损失数十亿美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 10:37:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/snowball-derivatives-feed-chinas-stock-market-avalanche-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国在联合国会议上罕见地接受人权记录审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-undergoes-rare-scrutiny-rights-record-un-meeting-2024-01-23/</link><description>周二，中国在联合国一次重要会议上接受了对其人权记录的审查，西方国家呼吁对新疆维吾尔人提供更多保护，并在香港提供更大自由，而北京则表示已取得历史性进展。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 10:06:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-undergoes-rare-scrutiny-rights-record-un-meeting-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>美国银行在亚洲裁员20人，中国投资银行家受影响最大——消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-america-cuts-20-investment-bankers-asia-sources-2024-01-23/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，美国银行周二宣布在亚洲裁员约 20 名银行家，原因是中国和香港市场暴跌打压了交易前景。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 10:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-america-cuts-20-investment-bankers-asia-sources-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>尽管减持复星仍将继续支持葡萄牙Millennium BCP</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/fosun-keep-supporting-portugals-millennium-bcp-despite-stake-cut-2024-01-23/</link><description>复星发言人周二表示，尽管减持了葡萄牙千禧银行的股份，但复星仍对葡萄牙市场持乐观态度，因此将继续支持葡萄牙千禧银行的发展。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 09:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/fosun-keep-supporting-portugals-millennium-bcp-despite-stake-cut-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲央行政策决定前谨慎，欧洲股市下跌，矿业股上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-flat-losses-healthcare-outweigh-miners-2024-01-23/</link><description>欧洲股市周二小幅走低，因投资者在欧洲央行 (ECB) 本周晚些时候的政策会议之前保持谨慎态度，而矿业股的上涨限制了进一步的下跌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 08:40:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-flat-losses-healthcare-outweigh-miners-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国希望联合国对人权的审查是建设性的、非政治化的</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hopes-un-review-human-rights-constructive-non-politicised-2024-01-23/</link><description>中国外交部周二表示，希望联合国各方以“建设性”和“非政治化”的方式审查中国的人权记录。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 07:58:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hopes-un-review-human-rights-constructive-non-politicised-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国采取措施支撑股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/measures-china-has-taken-prop-up-its-stock-market-2024-01-23/</link><description>彭博新闻社报道称，中国当局正在考虑采取多项措施来提振股市，中国股市周二反弹。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 07:15:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/measures-china-has-taken-prop-up-its-stock-market-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>投资者对中国市场崩溃的看法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/what-investors-are-saying-about-chinas-market-meltdown-2024-01-23/</link><description>中国和香港股市本周跌至多年低点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 05:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/what-investors-are-saying-about-chinas-market-meltdown-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>德国总统与企业访问越南寻求投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/german-president-businesses-visit-vietnam-eyeing-labour-deal-investment-2024-01-23/</link><description>德国商业代表团包括隧道机械、风力发电场和工业供应领域的顶级公司，与总统施泰因迈尔一起于周二开始对越南进行访问，柏林致力于减少对中国的依赖。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 05:36:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/german-president-businesses-visit-vietnam-eyeing-labour-deal-investment-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡亚洲创世纪 (Asia Genesis) 在押注中国和日本失败后关闭对冲基金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/singapores-asia-genesis-closes-hedge-fund-after-losing-bets-china-japan-2024-01-23/</link><description>总部位于新加坡的亚洲创世纪资产管理公司(Asia Genesis Asset Management)正在清算其对冲基金，该基金在中国和日本押注失误后出现了“前所未有的大幅缩水”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 05:34:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/singapores-asia-genesis-closes-hedge-fund-after-losing-bets-china-japan-2024-01-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>